    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hi there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty ride. It\u2019s been such a reliable companion and is still in really wonderful shape! Perfect for daily commutes or weekend trips. It\u2019s clean, well-maintained, and ready to hit the road with you. I\u2019m sad to see it go, but I know you\u2019ll love it as much as I have! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
