    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a well-sorted 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, equipped with individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system. This example utilizes the desirable Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox, delivering power through a torque-sensing limited-slip differential. The chassis remains taut with its signature 50/50 weight distribution; notably, the rear subframe has been reinforced and the VANOS system serviced\u2014essential preventative measures for this platform. While showing signs of spirited use consistent with its age, the mechanical synchronization between the throttle response and the MacPherson/multi-link suspension geometry remains sharp. A driver-focused machine for those who appreciate linear power delivery and telepathic steering feedback.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Regularly serviced. Clean interior. Reliable engine. Title in hand.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
