    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "This expertly maintained vehicle offers a distinguished combination of performance and long-term reliability. Presenting in commendable condition, the automobile features a well-preserved interior and a robust mechanical profile, ensuring a premium experience for its next owner. A testament to consistent care and engineering excellence, this model represents a superior acquisition for the discerning driver who values both substance and sophistication.",
      "price": 34500.0,
